secondary_street_name: Craven Park, Guilsborough Close, Bishops Way
description: Revised proposal for redevelopment of Phase 3, 4 and 5 (Site bounded by Church Road, Craven Park, Guilsborough Close, Bishop Way) of the resiform estate including 264 homes for social rent and 178 homes for private sale, comprising 160 one-bed flats, 152 two-bed flats, 20 two-bed houses, 83 three-bedroom houses, 25 four-bedroom houses, 2 five-bedroom houses and community centre, open spaces and new road layout.
